################################################################################
#                                                                              #     
#   Aruba ignores NTP Leap second flag and do not add the additional second.   # 
#   The time is adjusted at the next NTP update.                               #
#                                                                              #
################################################################################


1. To buld NTP ignoring leap second, please use "CONFIG_IGNORELEAP" under BUILD.platform script.

2. As of the BUILD.porfidio has been updated with this config.

